title: South Indian Temple In Rishikesh....
review: If you are enough of Ganga river and north Indian temple in Rishikesh, this Chandramouleswara Swamy Temple will be a big change for you. I felt like it's built properly in south Indian style and interesting. It's one the way from Rishikesh bus stand to ram jhula.

title: lord shiva
review: a small south indianstyle temple dedicated to lord shiva on the way to ram jhula. look out for the board as it is easy to miss.
